HEADWORD: Plaguy
<hw>Pla"guy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Vexatious;
troublesome; tormenting; <as>as, a <ex>plaguy</ex> horse</as>.
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark> Also used adverbially; <as>as, ⟦ldquo⟧He is so
<ex>plaguy</ex> proud</as>.⟦rdquo⟧</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Plaice</ent>⟦br⟧
